How to install and run Corona on Linux:

1) download Corona-Linux-x86-64-2018.XXXX.tar.gz

2) unpack .tar.gz file, for example
mkdir ~/CoronaSimulator
tar -xzf /tmp/Corona-Linux-x86-64-2018.XXXX.tar.gz -C ~/CoronaSimulator	

3) launch install-dependencies.sh
it will install all dependencies and Android SDK required by offline Android Builder

4) run start.sh

